We all know the character of Joan of Arc. Here is one of the many statues of Joan of Arc, represented in Paris.

Joan of Arc! It is the 2nd statue I have seen in Paris (the first very close to the Louvre). For those who know its history, it will be more valuable to find it in these small squares (and not in the center of a large one)
